<!-- ── Filter row ── -->
<div class="filter-row">
  <div class="filter-row-inner">
    <span class="label">Filter</span>
    <button class="filter-btn active" data-loc="all">All locations</button>
    <button class="filter-btn" data-loc="ayutthaya">Ayutthaya</button>
    <button class="filter-btn" data-loc="lamphun">Lamphun</button>
    <button class="filter-btn" data-loc="bangkok">Bangkok HQ</button>
    <button class="filter-btn" data-loc="kohkong">Koh Kong</button>
    <button class="filter-btn" data-loc="jiaxing">Jiaxing</button>
    <button class="filter-btn" data-loc="ohio">Ohio</button>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ── Stories grid ── -->
<div class="stories-bg">
  <div class="stories-wrap">
    <div class="stories-grid" id="stories-grid">

      <article class="story-card" data-loc="ayutthaya">
        <div class="story-photo">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1"><circle cx="12" cy="8" r="4"/><path d="M4 21c0-4 4-7 8-7s8 3 8 7"/></svg>
          <span class="photo-label">Photo 1</span>
        </div>
        <div class="story-body">
          <p class="story-quote">I started on the line and now I'm leading process improvements across three SMT cells. Hana gave me the training and the space to grow.</p>
          <div class="story-meta">
            <div class="story-person"><div class="name">Pim Suwannakij</div><div class="role">Process Engineer</div></div>
            <div class="story-place"><span class="story-chip">Ayutthaya</span><span class="story-year">Joined 2017</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <a href="#" class="read-more">Read full story →</a>
      </article>

      <article class="story-card" data-loc="lamphun">
        <div class="story-photo">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1"><circle cx="12" cy="8" r="4"/><path d="M4 21c0-4 4-7 8-7s8 3 8 7"/></svg>
          <span class="photo-label">Photo 2</span>
        </div>
        <div class="story-body">
          <p class="story-quote">What I love about Lamphun is how supportive the team is. Everyone shares what they know — there's no gatekeeping. That's how you learn fast.</p>
          <div class="story-meta">
            <div class="story-person"><div class="name">Nattaporn Saetang</div><div class="role">SMT Operator</div></div>
            <div class="story-place"><span class="story-chip">Lamphun</span><span class="story-year">Joined 2020</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <a href="#" class="read-more">Read full story →</a>
      </article>

      <article class="story-card" data-loc="ayutthaya">
        <div class="story-photo">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1"><circle cx="12" cy="8" r="4"/><path d="M4 21c0-4 4-7 8-7s8 3 8 7"/></svg>
          <span class="photo-label">Photo 3</span>
        </div>
        <div class="story-body">
          <p class="story-quote">Every NPI project is different. One week it's a wireless charging module, next week it's an automotive sensor. You're always learning.</p>
          <div class="story-meta">
            <div class="story-person"><div class="name">Somchai Ratchada</div><div class="role">NPI Engineer</div></div>
            <div class="story-place"><span class="story-chip">Ayutthaya</span><span class="story-year">Joined 2019</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <a href="#" class="read-more">Read full story →</a>
      </article>

      <article class="story-card" data-loc="bangkok">
        <div class="story-photo">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1"><circle cx="12" cy="8" r="4"/><path d="M4 21c0-4 4-7 8-7s8 3 8 7"/></svg>
          <span class="photo-label">Photo 4</span>
        </div>
        <div class="story-body">
          <p class="story-quote">The variety of customers we support from Bangkok keeps the work fresh. One day you're talking automotive, the next it's medical devices.</p>
          <div class="story-meta">
            <div class="story-person"><div class="name">Apinya Boonmee</div><div class="role">Customer Account Manager</div></div>
            <div class="story-place"><span class="story-chip">Bangkok HQ</span><span class="story-year">Joined 2015</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <a href="#" class="read-more">Read full story →</a>
      </article>

      <article class="story-card" data-loc="kohkong">
        <div class="story-photo">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1"><circle cx="12" cy="8" r="4"/><path d="M4 21c0-4 4-7 8-7s8 3 8 7"/></svg>
          <span class="photo-label">Photo 5</span>
        </div>
        <div class="story-body">
          <p class="story-quote">When the Koh Kong site opened, I was one of the first hires. Watching it grow from an empty hall to a full assembly facility has been incredible.</p>
          <div class="story-meta">
            <div class="story-person"><div class="name">Sokha Phon</div><div class="role">Production Supervisor</div></div>
            <div class="story-place"><span class="story-chip">Koh Kong</span><span class="story-year">Joined 2014</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <a href="#" class="read-more">Read full story →</a>
      </article>

      <article class="story-card" data-loc="ayutthaya">
        <div class="story-photo">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1"><circle cx="12" cy="8" r="4"/><path d="M4 21c0-4 4-7 8-7s8 3 8 7"/></svg>
          <span class="photo-label">Photo 6</span>
        </div>
        <div class="story-body">
          <p class="story-quote">I joined Hana straight out of university through the scholarship programme. Six years later, I'm running my own OSAT line.</p>
          <div class="story-meta">
            <div class="story-person"><div class="name">Thanawat Phromchai</div><div class="role">OSAT Line Lead</div></div>
            <div class="story-place"><span class="story-chip">Ayutthaya</span><span class="story-year">Joined 2019</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <a href="#" class="read-more">Read full story →</a>
      </article>

      <article class="story-card" data-loc="lamphun">
        <div class="story-photo">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1"><circle cx="12" cy="8" r="4"/><path d="M4 21c0-4 4-7 8-7s8 3 8 7"/></svg>
          <span class="photo-label">Photo 7</span>
        </div>
        <div class="story-body">
          <p class="story-quote">The Lamphun site feels like home. Many of us come from the local community — when we say we're growing together, we mean it.</p>
          <div class="story-meta">
            <div class="story-person"><div class="name">Wirat Khampan</div><div class="role">Quality Technician</div></div>
            <div class="story-place"><span class="story-chip">Lamphun</span><span class="story-year">Joined 2012</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <a href="#" class="read-more">Read full story →</a>
      </article>

      <article class="story-card" data-loc="bangkok">
        <div class="story-photo">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1"><circle cx="12" cy="8" r="4"/><path d="M4 21c0-4 4-7 8-7s8 3 8 7"/></svg>
          <span class="photo-label">Photo 8</span>
        </div>
        <div class="story-body">
          <p class="story-quote">Working in HR at Hana, I see every part of the business. From recruiting fresh graduates to running our scholarship programme, it's all connected.</p>
          <div class="story-meta">
            <div class="story-person"><div class="name">Kanyarat Chaiyaphum</div><div class="role">HR Business Partner</div></div>
            <div class="story-place"><span class="story-chip">Bangkok HQ</span><span class="story-year">Joined 2018</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <a href="#" class="read-more">Read full story →</a>
      </article>

      <article class="story-card" data-loc="ayutthaya">
        <div class="story-photo">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1"><circle cx="12" cy="8" r="4"/><path d="M4 21c0-4 4-7 8-7s8 3 8 7"/></svg>
          <span class="photo-label">Photo 9</span>
        </div>
        <div class="story-body">
          <p class="story-quote">I came in as a junior test engineer. Now I lead the test department at Ayutthaya. The path was clear, and the support was real.</p>
          <div class="story-meta">
            <div class="story-person"><div class="name">Patcharin Sukhum</div><div class="role">Test Engineering Manager</div></div>
            <div class="story-place"><span class="story-chip">Ayutthaya</span><span class="story-year">Joined 2011</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <a href="#" class="read-more">Read full story →</a>
      </article>

      <article class="story-card" data-loc="jiaxing">
        <div class="story-photo">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1"><circle cx="12" cy="8" r="4"/><path d="M4 21c0-4 4-7 8-7s8 3 8 7"/></svg>
          <span class="photo-label">Photo 10</span>
        </div>
        <div class="story-body">
          <p class="story-quote">Jiaxing is where Hana's group standards meet the speed of the China market. You learn to move quickly without cutting corners on quality.</p>
          <div class="story-meta">
            <div class="story-person"><div class="name">Liu Wei</div><div class="role">RFID Process Engineer</div></div>
            <div class="story-place"><span class="story-chip">Jiaxing</span><span class="story-year">Joined 2016</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <a href="#" class="read-more">Read full story →</a>
      </article>

      <article class="story-card" data-loc="ohio">
        <div class="story-photo">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1"><circle cx="12" cy="8" r="4"/><path d="M4 21c0-4 4-7 8-7s8 3 8 7"/></svg>
          <span class="photo-label">Photo 11</span>
        </div>
        <div class="story-body">
          <p class="story-quote">The Ohio site is small but specialised. We design and build the RFID tire tags running on highways across North America. That's something to be proud of.</p>
          <div class="story-meta">
            <div class="story-person"><div class="name">Mike Reynolds</div><div class="role">RFID Engineering Lead</div></div>
            <div class="story-place"><span class="story-chip">Ohio</span><span class="story-year">Joined 2010</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <a href="#" class="read-more">Read full story →</a>
      </article>

    </div>
    <div class="stories-empty" id="stories-empty">No stories from this location yet — check back soon.</div>
  </div>
</div>

